  "instructions": [
    "In a bowl, combine cooked farro, diced roasted bell pepper, and pitted dates.",
    "Whisk lime juice, olive oil, chili powder, smoked paprika, black pepper, and sea salt until well mixed.",
    "Add tahini and pasta water; whisk vigorously until a creamy emulsion forms.",
    "Pour the sauce over the farro mixture and toss until fully coated.",
    "Sprinkle chopped cilantro over the bowl and drizzle additional lime juice if desired.",
    "Serve immediately, optionally garnish with extra chili flakes or a squeeze of lime."
